  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read architecture §8.3 (citation enforcement model) for the canonical persona text.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `PlaybookChatContextProvider.cs` to understand the persona-injection seam (especially line 130-154 mentioned in architecture §6.2).</step>
    <step order="3">Define `ITrustFrameInstructionInjector` + `BuildAsync` signature.</step>
    <step order="4">Implement:
      - Constant base text from architecture §8.3 (verbatim seed)
      - Conditional condensation: if session has zero uploaded files, drop the file-specific paragraph
      - Output deterministic + byte-stable for cache-hit support</step>
    <step order="5">Author unit test: assert verbatim base text + condensation logic + byte-stability across two calls with same context.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `dotnet build` + `dotnet test`.</step>
    <step order="7">Measure BFF publish size.</step>
    <step order="8">code-review + adr-check.</step>
